        {
            "title": "颱風麥德姆逼近 廣東省湛江市對全市實行「五停」指令",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 根據一份政府通告，隨著颱風「<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:麥德姆;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/麥德姆\">麥德姆</a>」逼近，廣東省湛江市計畫於10月4日起在湛江市全域範圍內分批次採取「五停」措施即：停課、停工、停產、停運、停業。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據氣象部門監測預報，「麥德姆」將於10月5日白天以颱風至強颱風級在粵西到海南島東部沿海登陸，正面襲擊雷州半島的可能性較大</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4日夜間至6日白天湛江市將有一次暴雨到大暴雨、局部特大暴雨的降水過程</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">各類市場、商場、餐飲娛樂場所、公園景區、沿街商鋪、會展行業等將停止營業</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">注：央視：中國因颱風麥德姆啟動重大氣象災害三級應急響應</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">注：颱風麥德姆登陸菲律賓強度增強 預計將移向中國</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Zhanjiang Suspends Most Activities as Typhoon Approaches</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-281023f0-aa5b-3c5e-959c-c6dce374e816-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%A7%86%E9%80%BC%E8%BF%91-%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%9C%81%E6%B9%9B%E6%B1%9F%E5%B8%82%E5%B0%8D%E5%85%A8%E5%B8%82%E5%AF%A6%E8%A1%8C-%E4%BA%94%E5%81%9C-%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4-082047494.html",
