        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利：美國國債期權顯示政府停擺可長達29天",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"摩根士丹利：美國國債期權顯示政府停擺可長達29天\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hyuAR2DR4ay7sgB6TmQcvw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/64b98020-a0c7-11f0-bdbf-638f00d1c178\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">摩根士丹利：美國國債期權顯示政府停擺可長達29天</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E6%9C%9F%E6%AC%8A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%81%9C%E6%93%BA%E5%8F%AF%E9%95%B7%E9%81%9429%E5%A4%A9-174452167.html",
